Subject: [minstrels] Poem #1831: Dana Gioia
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=ISO-8859-1
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 7bit
X-Virus-Scanned: ClamAV 0.87.1/1347/Tue Mar 21 08:35:25 2006 on phobos
