Subject: [minstrels] Poem #1848: Phil Ochs
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=ISO-8859-1
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
X-Virus-Scanned: ClamAV 0.87.1/1392/Tue Apr 11 10:28:12 2006 on phobos
